FlowSimpleDetailsForm is a Form
    title is "ProcessDefinition"
    restrict action Delete
        when (FlowType.SystemDefined)
    Layout
        two column
            PfiFlowDefinition
            visible when (not FlowType.SystemDefined)
                FlowType
                    display only
                CurrentFlowVersion
                    display only
                visible when (AutoRestartInXmlToggle)
                    AutoRestartText
            IsSubProcess
                display only
            Description
            IsFlowEnabled
            two column
                FlowLogLevel
